<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 10:08:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>塔梅尔在纳布卢斯志愿担任护理人员。他在执行任务时被以色列导弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/tamer-was-a-volunteer-paramedic-he-was-killed-in-the-line-of-duty-by-an-israeli-missile/00000191-5e7a-d017-abd9-fffe803d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦难民营的一名 21 岁志愿护理人员被以色列导弹炸死，尽管他身穿表明自己是医务人员的橙色背心。他在他姐姐计划举行婚礼的那天去世了。自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军也加大了对约旦河西岸的空袭力度</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 04:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/tamer-was-a-volunteer-paramedic-he-was-killed-in-the-line-of-duty-by-an-israeli-missile/00000191-5e7a-d017-abd9-fffe803d0000</guid></item><item><title>即使政府腐败，这个组织也能拯救以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-when-the-government-is-corrupt-this-group-can-save-israel/00000191-5e5d-db59-a5d1-7f5dc75b0000</link><description>2011年，摩萨德首脑阻止了轰炸伊朗的决定，但到了2024年，国防领域已经没有人像梅尔·达甘那样能阻止内塔尼亚胡了。有骨气的专业人士可以使以色列免遭全面战争、民主制度的破坏以及香蕉共和国的转型</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:55:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-when-the-government-is-corrupt-this-group-can-save-israel/00000191-5e5d-db59-a5d1-7f5dc75b0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们永远无法在极端分子的主场击败他们。中间派必须做完全相反的事情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/well-never-defeat-extremists-in-their-home-court-centrists-must-do-the-exact-opposite/00000191-5e29-dd29-a7f3-7f696e770000</link><description>超过 30 名政治家、知识分子、学者和作家共同撰写了一本新书，该书由 Yair Lapid 的高级政策顾问编辑，解释了为什么中间主义是治疗极端主义的良方</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/well-never-defeat-extremists-in-their-home-court-centrists-must-do-the-exact-opposite/00000191-5e29-dd29-a7f3-7f696e770000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩报道：以色列袭击造成 10 人死亡；以色列国防军下令撤离加沙居民区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-live/.premium/lebanese-reports-6-killed-3-wounded-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-southern-lebanon/00000191-5e13-d180-a9fd-dffb39660000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道：以色列对加沙中部难民营的袭击造成 12 人死亡 ■ 拜登表示，他指示多哈谈判小组提出周五提出的提案 ■ 哈马斯高级官员：“最新一轮会谈中没有就重大问题达成一致” ■加沙卫生部表示，在加沙地带发现了首例脊髓灰质炎病例</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 02:22:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-live/.premium/lebanese-reports-6-killed-3-wounded-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-southern-lebanon/00000191-5e13-d180-a9fd-dffb39660000</guid></item><item><title>调查显示定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄时以色列国防军部队袖手旁观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</link><description>一名高级国防官员说，士兵们“没有采取任何行动来阻止大屠杀，他们只是站在旁边，看到了一切，却什么也没做。”被杀巴勒斯坦人的尸体已被送往尸检，但结果无法确定是谁射杀了他</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</guid></item><item><title>尽管发生了战争，议会平民准备委员会已经几个月没有召开会议了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-knesset-committee-on-civilian-preparedness-hasnt-convened-for-months/00000191-5b80-d101-a7fd-7bbf13a30000</link><description>消息人士称，由于委员会讨论的议题较多，除了小组委员会的密切监督和深入讨论外，别无选择，距离小组委员会上次召开会议已经过去了四个月，这危及了以色列的国家安全</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 18:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-knesset-committee-on-civilian-preparedness-hasnt-convened-for-months/00000191-5b80-d101-a7fd-7bbf13a30000</guid></item><item><title>“像我这样的犹太人不再在左派中感到受欢迎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-like-me-no-longer-feel-welcome-on-the-left/00000191-50e4-d50b-adff-72e792a50000</link><description>对于澳大利亚最著名的记者之一、前自称为“反犹太复国主义崩得”的迈克尔·加文达来说，10 月 7 日是一个警钟。随着他的祖国反犹太主义的高涨，特别是在他曾经视为盟友的群体中，他担心澳大利亚的犹太人</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-like-me-no-longer-feel-welcome-on-the-left/00000191-50e4-d50b-adff-72e792a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自以为强大，但从未如此依赖美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-thinks-its-strong-but-has-never-been-so-dependent-on-the-u-s/00000191-5b22-d392-a995-7fe6d4e10000</link><description>自10月7日以来，美国除了提供大规模军事援助外，还三度向中东派遣主力部队，帮助以色列对抗伊朗及其代理人。这是关系的悖论：在内塔尼亚胡的领导下，以色列感觉越强大，就越依赖美国</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-thinks-its-strong-but-has-never-been-so-dependent-on-the-u-s/00000191-5b22-d392-a995-7fe6d4e10000</guid></item><item><title>调解人称，美国提出停火提议，在以色列和哈马斯之间架起桥梁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presents-cease-fire-proposal-that-bridges-israel-hamas-mediators-say/00000191-5bb4-d101-a7fd-7bbfda890000</link><description>据调解员称，该提案“有助于迅速实施协议” ■ 预计谈判将于下周在开罗继续进行</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presents-cease-fire-proposal-that-bridges-israel-hamas-mediators-say/00000191-5bb4-d101-a7fd-7bbfda890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 315 天：拜登称谈判各方“比以往任何时候都更接近”停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-315-biden-says-negotiating-parties-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire/00000191-5bff-dc4c-a59f-7bff300f0001</link><description>停火/人质释放协议的谈判周五在卡塔尔继续进行，一位消息人士称，他们“到目前为止已经取得了成功” ■ 接近真主党的消息人士告诉《华盛顿邮报》，只要谈判正在进行，真主党就不会报复以色列多哈 ■ 以色列外长告诉英国和法国外长，“如果伊朗发动袭击，我们预计联军不仅会与以色列一起防御” ■ 战争已过去 315 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-315-biden-says-negotiating-parties-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire/00000191-5bff-dc4c-a59f-7bff300f0001</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯人质的父亲说：“如果内塔尼亚胡想要达成协议，这次采访就不会进行”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</link><description>伊齐克·霍恩（Itzik Horn）花了数周时间并承受巨大压力才得知他的两个儿子亚伊尔（Yair）和埃坦（Eitan）被关押在加沙。这位阿根廷出生的父亲猛烈抨击那些“背着人质”为加沙带来秩序的人，并建议内塔尼亚胡派他的儿子亚伊尔前往加沙，带回霍恩的儿子亚伊尔</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日已经足够令人震惊了。以色列人为何要粉饰这场悲剧？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</guid></item><item><title>美国殖民地酒店希望成为一座理智的岛屿。随后加沙战争爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-american-colony-hotel-hoped-to-be-an-island-of-sanity-then-the-war-broke-out/00000191-5b57-d761-afd9-7f576bf10000</link><description>该酒店是耶路撒冷的地标，但由于入住率直线下降，其生存在其 100 年历史中首次面临危险</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 13:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-american-colony-hotel-hoped-to-be-an-island-of-sanity-then-the-war-broke-out/00000191-5b57-d761-afd9-7f576bf10000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室数据显示，截至 10 月 7 日，内塔尼亚胡已出国六次，花费超过 600 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/until-oct-7-netanyahu-flew-abroad-six-times-at-cost-of-over-6-million-pmo-data-shows/00000191-5afa-d101-a7fd-7aff08c70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在巴黎、罗马和柏林的停留各持续三天，其中巴黎的费用最高，花费了纳税人100万美元。罗马的旅行费用约为 50 万美元，柏林的旅行费用为 302,000 美元</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 12:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/until-oct-7-netanyahu-flew-abroad-six-times-at-cost-of-over-6-million-pmo-data-shows/00000191-5afa-d101-a7fd-7aff08c70000</guid></item><item><title>世界必须做出决定：执行加沙授权还是让中东的流血事件继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-world-must-decide-implement-gaza-mandate-or-let-the-bloodshed-in-the-region-continue/00000191-5a0a-d753-a395-dbeba59f0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构没有能力治理加沙，以色列唯一有战后计划的是那些支持吞并的人。虽然让加沙重返托管时代听起来像是另一次殖民主义干预的开始，但事实上，国际机构已经在管理加沙地带</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 09:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-world-must-decide-implement-gaza-mandate-or-let-the-bloodshed-in-the-region-continue/00000191-5a0a-d753-a395-dbeba59f0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太定居者袭击西岸村庄；巴勒斯坦人死亡，一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</link><description>周四晚上，数十名犹太定居者突然袭击吉特，造成至少一人死亡；亚伊尔·戈兰：“定居者是一个暴力团体，得到政府的大力支持”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 07:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火、人质谈判将于周五继续；卡塔尔总理向伊朗通报了谈判进展情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-hostage-talks-to-continue-friday-qatari-pm-updated-iran-on-progress/00000191-59a8-db91-a7dd-7fa8abb50000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，“双方希望在未来 24 小时内看到进展”。伊朗还收到了谈判的最新情况，表明伊朗间接参与了谈判，以及美国、卡塔尔和埃及为防止伊朗和真主党升级而做出的努力</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 06:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-hostage-talks-to-continue-friday-qatari-pm-updated-iran-on-progress/00000191-59a8-db91-a7dd-7fa8abb50000</guid></item><item><title>“现在，在以色列，人们已经撤离家园。但我们从一个星球搬到了另一个星球”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/now-many-israelis-have-evacuated-their-homes-but-we-moved-from-one-planet-to-another/00000191-5929-d316-a9f1-dde9fd4c0000</link><description>她经历过失落、拒绝和局外人的痛苦，但从未离开过舞台。 94 岁高龄的以色列剧院第一夫人 Lea Koenig 谈论如何才能过上长久而有意义的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 04:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/now-many-israelis-have-evacuated-their-homes-but-we-moved-from-one-planet-to-another/00000191-5929-d316-a9f1-dde9fd4c0000</guid></item><item><title>“当我从我的与生俱来的权利之旅回到家时，我将开始去犹太教堂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-16/ty-article/.highlight/when-i-get-back-home-from-my-birthright-trip-ill-start-going-to-synagogue/00000191-592a-d316-a9f1-ddeab4d10000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位从小就信奉天主教的美国人在以色列之行中学到了很多东西，而一位以色列人则因为“神灵把他送到那里”而进入萨满教</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:40:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-16/ty-article/.highlight/when-i-get-back-home-from-my-birthright-trip-ill-start-going-to-synagogue/00000191-592a-d316-a9f1-ddeab4d10000</guid></item><item><title>美国人正在发放胡萝卜，但内塔尼亚胡更担心国内的大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-americans-are-handing-out-carrots-but-netanyahus-more-worried-about-sticks-at-home/00000191-56da-dc4c-a59f-7eff397e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的所有考虑因素在多哈发生冲突 ■ 美国人对以色列对哈马斯的破坏程度感到惊讶，但相信它已经取得了所能做到的一切 ■ 真主党与以色列建立了恐惧平衡，但也处于劣势</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-americans-are-handing-out-carrots-but-netanyahus-more-worried-about-sticks-at-home/00000191-56da-dc4c-a59f-7eff397e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>